工作职责:
1. As a global digital trainee of H World, you need to understand global hotel operations & management systems, output and execute test cases based on product design documents to ensure product delivery quality; 
2. Responsible for communicating between domestic R&D teams and overseas digital teams to develop test plan, and drive the test execution effectively;
3. Support the domestic R&D teams within the global digitization project, promote the product and R&D staff to fix the defects and ensure the on-time product delivery, while collaborating with the overseas team for user acceptance testing;Coordinate the test dependencies on other products to ensure a successful end-to-end function integration after products go live.

1、作为华住集团全球数字化的测试人员，了解酒店运营管理相关系统并根据产品文档设计测试用例并执行测试，确保产品交付质量;负责与国内产品研发团队以及海外数字化团队沟通，制定测试计划和测试方案，并有效推进测试执行；
2、根据全球数字化项目进度，支持国内研发条线，推动产品和研发人员进行缺陷修复，确保产品按时上线，同时协同海外团队进行用户验收测试；
3、协调其他平行产线中的测试依赖项，确保上线后端对端功能集成正确。

任职资格:
1. Graduated between 2022/01 and 2023/07, bachelor's degree or above, overseas experience preferred;
2. Strong problem analysis ability, logical thinking ability, communication ability and learning ability;
3. Good Oral and written English skills for communicating and coordinating with overseas for requirement output;
4. Computer science, software engineering, information management and other related majors are preferred.

1、在2022年1月-2023年7月间毕业的海内外优秀学子，本科及以上学历，有海外留学或者生活经历者优先；
2、较强的问题分析能力、逻辑思考能力，较强的沟通能力、学习能力；
3、口语及书面英文好，负责与海外进行沟通协调，进行需求产出；
4、计算机，软件工程，信息管理等相关专业优先。
